FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our crypto transaction app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What cryptocurrencies does your app support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app supports a wide range of popular cryptocurrencies, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, and many more. We're constantly adding new coins to our platform.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How secure are transactions on your app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We prioritize security with state-of-the-art encryption, two-factor authentication, and cold storage for funds. Your transactions and assets are protected by industry-leading security measures.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What are the fees for using your crypto transaction app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Our fee structure is transparent and competitive. We charge a small percentage on each transaction, with discounts for high-volume users. Check our pricing page for detailed information.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How fast are transactions processed on your platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Transaction speed varies depending on the cryptocurrency and network congestion. Most transactions are confirmed within minutes, but we also offer options for expedited processing.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I use your app internationally?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, our app is available globally. We support multiple languages and currencies, allowing you to manage your crypto transactions from anywhere in the world, subject to local regulations.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, there are small transaction fees associated with using our app. These fees vary depending on the type of cryptocurrency and the nature of the transaction.
